    body: "Hang a sauna-rated door (tempered glass or insulated wood) that opens outward, fit the thermometer/hygrometer and any controller, and add a sauna-rated light. Run a first heat-up with the room empty and well ventilated to burn off manufacturing residue before your first real session. Then estimate running cost and double-check your budget with the <a href=\"/tools/sauna-cost-calculator/\">cost calculator</a>.",
